title: Cloudy Day R&B
description:
Been messing around with some playlists and mixes.  It's a cloudy Saturday afternoon and I think this is a good soundtrack for it.  Enjoy.

Check out my site btraven.org and drop me an email if you've got any suggestions for mixes.

Peace and Love,

B.T.
